You should use zipWithIndex feature on scala collections (more information in scala documentation: [here][1]);

Exaple use:

```
@for((value, index) &lt;- list.zipWithIndex){

  @* Print value *@
  @value 

  @* Print index - first index will be 0 *@
  @index

  @* Print index + 1 *@
  @{index+1}

}



```

  [1]: https://www.scala-lang.org/api/current/scala/collection/View$$ZipWithIndex.html

